{"id": 93, "genre": 1000, "title": "出门旅行，你无法忍受的旅伴？", "description": "生活研究所每周都会推出当季应景并充满正义感的“无！法！忍！受！”小调查，欢迎来表态。", "record_count": 2839, "comment_count": 10, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160607194541OnA1xRPwtqLs0chM.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2014-09-30T08:20:22Z", "questions": [{"id": 95, "title": "出门旅行，你无法忍受的旅伴？", "content": "出门旅行，你无法忍受的旅伴？", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 817, "content": "自己不做攻略，又对别人的攻略很嫌弃", "image": "img/option/option/201606061618331FhPdvb49OgcYAaR.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 818, "content": "在著名景点前排队照相比V字", "image": "img/option/option/20160606161833HBJoZ3xmg4WGQ5Kf.png", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 819, "content": "一定要排队进人很多的景点", "image": "img/option/option/201606061618344iPnLRcVqZxaNBAF.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 820, "content": "不懂当地文化但一定要发表见解", "image": "img/option/option/20160606161834YHQuxT7Sjanq89D5.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 821, "content": "觉得冲锋衣可以应付一切场合", "image": "img/option/option/20160606161834wdis2hgkaLrGRy7D.jpeg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 822, "content": "旅行中记账太清楚", "image": "img/option/option/20160606161834eFqz0OGYI6vnNfwT.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 823, "content": "生活不能自理，要你帮忙带牙膏防晒等任何东西", "image": "img/option/option/20160606161835XtphIJer3vNHC0S4.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 824, "content": "诡异方向感，坚持自己认为的东方才是东方", "image": "img/option/option/20160606161835YLQBFJWp7uGTI8DA.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 825, "content": "啥啥都不能吃", "image": "img/option/option/20160606161835I1zGDxsOQAtbauSH.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 826, "content": "跟着到处走，但看啥都没意思", "image": "img/option/option/20160606161835ObECMkINeh4FuB75.jpeg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 827, "content": "对世界太有